data.description: Don’t miss your chance to own a classic ranch-style home in a convenient Pensacola location! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is within walking distance to Oakfield Acres Park. As you arrive, you’ll immediately notice the beautifully landscaped corner lot with a beautiful oak tree providing plenty of shade in the front yard, plus the large covered front porch with plenty of room for your rocking chairs. Step inside and find the original hardwood floors throughout most of the home, and plantation shutters throughout the main living areas. There is a large family room which flows straight in the recently remodeled kitchen that has plenty of cabinet and counter space, as well as a newer stainless steel range and dishwasher. Off the kitchen, you will find a recently remodeled walk through pantry that leads right into the indoor laundry room. Down the hall, you will find the 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. All 3 bedrooms have ceiling fans and offer plenty of closet space, and the master bath has updated tile tub/shower and floors while the guest bath has a walk-in shower. Step outside and imagine yourself enjoying peaceful summer evenings on the large concrete patio overlooking the large fully fenced backyard with well-maintained landscaping including sprinkler system with a well. This home has a large 2-car garage with lofted storage space, hurricane shutters, a tankless water heater, and all copper wiring. This home has also had many items upgraded in recent years, including a new roof in 2019, and new double-pane windows in 2021.
